{"tid":148090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"剪完頭髮後別人的目光","createTime":"2017-03-08T10:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T11:30:03.000Z","uid":9425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fde1885fde32b3dba5076a0265b4281769cba83","tid":148090,"uid":9425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:33:37.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>放左學著住件校服去剪頭髮<br />\n剪完之後通常個髮型師都問你gel唔gel<br />\n我就通常gel埋先走<br />\n諗住型一陣返屋企<br />\n點知係返屋企途中有好多人既目光<br />\n先望頭髮再望件校服<br />\n搞到我覺得好尷尬同埋好似好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係我無乜自信心<br />\n有冇巴打同我一樣有呢啲情況<br />\n定係直接唔gel返歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c188c818b8d623d7b46ad41ffa89797e1e1c81ab","tid":148090,"uid":45926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327040118a8f59aefd5ee00b402070f4dcc04522","tid":148090,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"巴打有得gel都好啲 之前想剪正常齊陰 條友剪左做眉上陰 戈日仲要無戴con 戴住副眼鏡成個智障咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129107c138686a6a6679517a6da2f6d76dd37d0f","tid":148090,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"毒"},{"pid":"e394a170cf5dfe3e530f71764f79fed9d4c8946f","tid":148090,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"Gel得好就係姐"},{"pid":"8dc3547c0d4e4aba83f8fdf2c63b004cde74cfdd","tid":148090,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"我從來唔會覺得俾人笑, 就算剪左頭髮後都唔會, <br />\n<br />\n樓主真係慘"},{"pid":"999a9747228407fd44f8d5b623e152808b117a13","tid":148090,"uid":9425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote